## **📝 Enhancements in This Version**

### 🔥 **1️⃣ Clickable "Go!" Links for Cleaner CSVs**

- **Old:** URLs cluttering the CSV 📝
- **New:** Every link now appears as **"Go!"** – fully clickable for streamlined navigation. 📎

### 🔥 **2️⃣ No More Garbled Text – UTF-8 Fixes**

- **Auto-detects and fixes encoding issues** using `chardet`.
- Ensures **consistent text formatting** in all scraped articles.

### 🔥 **3️⃣ Article Titles Stay Clean & Readable**

- **Limits headlines to 90 characters** to prevent messy or truncated text.
- Cuts off **non-essential information** while preserving clarity.

### 🔥 **4️⃣ Real-Time News Only – 3-Day Filter Applied**

- **Filters out older articles**, ensuring **only fresh, relevant news** is scraped.
- Eliminates outdated reports and redundant stories.

